ecentralized cloud is a cloud that is provided by people, for people. To scale out and deliver the exponential increase in required data processing and storage capabilities, a new model is needed â€“ a model in which people own servers and share these servers out to other people to use. This should be possible for individual people and companies. By many, for everyone.  ThreeFold Tech is building the technology to do this and the ThreeFold Foundation is promoting and marketing the TF Grid, <a href=\"https://threefold.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">the the largest peer-to-peer grid on the planet</a></p>\n<p>The opportunity is huge, as the cloud market is expanding at an exponential rate. Gartner forecasts the market turnover to be 350 Billion USD by the end of 2022.</p>\n<h2 id=\"the-threefold-grid\"><a href=\"#the-threefold-grid\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>The ThreeFold Grid</h2>\n<p>The ThreeFold Grid is the largest active decentralized cloud in the world.</p>\n<p>There is way too much to fit here! Check this link to find a lot of information: <a href=\"https://cloud.threefold.io\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ThreeFold Decentralized Grid</a></p>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 960 540' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-7e860e1416225fe95a27bca63366b64c'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-7e860e1416225fe95a27bca63366b64c)' width='960' height='540' xlink:href='data:image/png%3bbase64%2ciVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAEAAAAAkCAYAAAA5DDySAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAJCElEQVRo3r2aaW8bxxnH9TH9MfoZghhwiwJ5nXdFU7uAiySOZMu2jlgSqVumZMkiKVKkeN/3fT%2bZ3yyHZVWR2qWpLDCY5ezs/J/7WGlFZlyj0Wgyf%2buYPu%2bx61txp9%2b1c63YIWQecXaJX0QIs5hZpsBX7BJiruFwKE4vu8Q8JMRFz